      <dc:creator>Luke Heley</dc:creator>
      <link>https://lajh87.github.io/posts/2021-07-10-better-chroropleths-with-datashine</link>
      <description>This post is inspired by Oliver O'Brien &amp; James Cheshire (2016) DataShine 
application which overlays urban areas onto Choropleths so the data
shines through the map. Thereby overcomming a common shortfall with Choropleths
on areas with uneven population densities.</description>
